{"tid":2491984,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［日本戰國］毛利元就——係咪戰國最強大名","createTime":"2021-04-16T17:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:37:01.000Z","uid":51738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03d1d1c3d7dae9b78eaada3f9b7d299fe50ede02","tid":2491984,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"由世代相傳國人領主，要喺各大名之間掙扎求存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（西：大內氏，東：尼子氏、山名氏）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再擺脫從屬，同時將自己既仔滲透去其他家族度做當主擴大自家勢力/影響力（毛利兩川）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二仔 元春入主 吉川家<br />\n三仔 隆景入主 小早川家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後再同以往從屬過既大名打大交，再消滅埋佢地（大內、尼子家）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後成為超過一百萬石既中國霸主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊一開始國人領主嗰陣可能五千石都未必有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身家應該翻咗二百倍都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計石高翻倍應該仲多過織田信長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得遠少少，冇佢都冇推翻幕府既長州藩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未必有咁先進既日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21c59730c311a58f0808d2b7b31c01be9286e03","tid":2491984,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"戰國第一智障"},{"pid":"a68fb607560473e59c32287b5ad4f5dee3c82d8a","tid":2491984,"uid":119591,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"佢招大最屈 魔水都食暈<br />\n1，2技食兵<br />\n前期出支吹已經屠到對面走場<br />\n之後屌地冰書火書又殺到人又壓到塔 團戰大技控場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81263f5933e661b002e6e3fcb86daf016302026d","tid":2491984,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff9179e84930ea051fa8b32d8679926957ffc94","tid":2491984,"uid":24309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a68fb607560473e59c32287b5ad4f5dee3c82d8a","tid":2491984,"uid":119591,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"佢招大最屈 魔水都食暈<br />\n1，2技食兵<br />\n前期出支吹已經屠到對面走場<br />\n之後屌地冰書火書又殺到人又壓到塔 團戰大技控場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"開親大都閃到幾個等待連線"},{"pid":"7e6592dba38b694590190da4d700d639adcd1ba4","tid":2491984,"uid":40568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"閃完屌地冰計接大技<br />\n耶穌見到都要避一避"},{"pid":"5ea33212e8bed372e2ff11dd3eee03720cdcd22c","tid":2491984,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ff9179e84930ea051fa8b32d8679926957ffc94","tid":2491984,"uid":24309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a68fb607560473e59c32287b5ad4f5dee3c82d8a","tid":2491984,"uid":119591,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"佢招大最屈 魔水都食暈<br />\n1，2技食兵<br />\n前期出支吹已經屠到對面走場<br />\n之後屌地冰書火書又殺到人又壓到塔 團戰大技控場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re